headline: Q3 earnings could derail Q4 market gains
summary: Truist chief investment officer and chief market strategist Keith Lerner expects the market to continue to climb in the final quarter of 2025, but he tells Yahoo Finance earnings moderation could derail fourth quarter gains. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.

headline: Why First Financial Bancorp (FFBC) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of regional banking company First Financial Bancorp (NASDAQ:FFBC) jumped 2.8% in the afternoon session after Truist Securities raised its price target on the stock to $29 from $28, reflecting the company's planned acquisition of BankFinancial. While the firm maintained its "Hold" rating, the higher price target was based on integrating the BankFinancial deal into its financial model.
